Package org.neo4j.values.storable

Interface Generator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RandomGenerator, SplittableRandomGenerator
    public interface Generator
    This class is meant as a gap so that we don't need a direct dependency on a random number generator.

    For example by wrapping in a generator we can support both java.util.Random and java.util .SplittableRandom
